{"type": "article", "id": 13713, "title": "极简钱包", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-19T07:36:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021012136otExJ7NdfOMI1rY.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自美国明尼苏达州的 The Supr Good Co 一直以极简设计为主打，最近他们推出了一款名为 Slim 2 wallet 的小钱包，采用光滑的皮革，外部除其 Logo 外再无其他装饰，内部则采用了弹力带来稳定卡和现金，适合放在大口袋里面作为分层收纳使用。钱包目前有棕色，深灰色和浅灰色三种颜色可以选择，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/supr/slim-2-the-perfect-minimal-wallet\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。<a href=\"http://www.suprgood.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看 The Supr Good Co 的官方主页，了解他们更多产品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141428BqpIxcYOX62gMnzQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414283SEp5eAgBmYTNUs0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141429vMwQat3r5khTxyEX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141429O0DxIfo9zJX3iqVA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03235294\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141430YgSdcR8HqWVrOFsX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414307ifKsCIFd5gBkJwV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.28970588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141431LvgPHfVSDQ91pXWc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141431MBRIzOypVN2Sxdmo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141431qJOCYKIo6SsjuN8v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414320EuRhnG7MibJFXTk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614143241mVHEbDrF0ge2AW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"